'''牛膝菊'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Galinsoga parviflora''}}），又名辣子草、向阳花、珍珠草、铜锤草、小米菊，是[[菊科|菊科]][[牛膝菊属|牛膝菊属]]的植物。原產于[[南美洲|南美洲]]，哥倫比亞人會用它來烹製[[阿西亚科|阿西亚科]]<ref name="s">[http://www.b-and-t-world-seeds.com/86392.html B & T World Seeds, ''Tridax parviflora (Galinsoga parviflora)'' in Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.b-and-t-world-seeds.com/86392.html |date=20200919212333 }} includes photo plus recipe for soup containing this plant as an ingredient</ref>。 1796年被人從秘魯帶到[[邱園|邱園]]，一度被稱為邱草（Kew Weed）<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/805221553|title=Flora Britannica : supported by common ground|last=Lovett.|first=Jones, Gareth|last2=).|first2=Gibbons, Bob (1949-|publisher=Chatto & Windus|isbn=1856193772|oclc=805221553|access-date=2018-02-22|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320193417/https://www.worldcat.org/title/flora-britannica-supported-by-common-ground/oclc/805221553|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來擴散到世界各地<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.brc.ac.uk/plantatlas/index.php?q=plant/galinsoga-parviflora|title=Galinsoga parviflora (Gallant-soldier) {{!}} Online Atlas of the British and Irish Flora|website=www.brc.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2017-05-16|archive-date=2018-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714170055/http://www.brc.ac.uk/plantatlas/index.php?q=plant%2Fgalinsoga-parviflora|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cabi.org/isc/datasheet/25299 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331114517/http://www.cabi.org/isc/datasheet/25299 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，高度可達75釐米，開白色小花。<ref>Clapham, A.R., Tutin, T.G. and Warburg, E.F. 1968 ''Excursion Flora of the British Isles.'' Cambridge University Press. {{ISBN|0-521-04656-4}}</ref><ref name="x">{{Cite web |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200023969 |title=Flora of China, ''Galinsoga parviflora'' Cavanilles, 1795.  <big>牛膝菊</big> niu xi ju |access-date=2018-02-22 |arc